{"tid":1346344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國網民：元朗群眾厲害了！支持你們正義之舉","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T04:12:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"caf84c1e9e61e876e686fb88a9a9070069974933","tid":1346344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190722/large/1563764919_f575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190722%2Flarge%2F1563764919_f575.jpg&h=1e3e385c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大批相信是黑社會成員的白衣「暴徒」，無差別在港鐵元朗站及市內手持木棍打人，導至最少45人受傷，當中一人危殆，中國官媒沒有報道元朗黑社會打人，只報道昨晚中聯辦破壞。<br />\n<br />\n在中國微博，網民竟然對暴行一致叫好，大讚「元朗群眾厲害了」，聲稱白衣人不斷狂毆香港市民，是「大快人心事！內地人民支持你們的正義之舉！」更稱:「據說是港獨自己扮演演戲！」<br />\n<br />\n不少中國網民轉載白衣暴徒狂無差別打人的照片，中國網民這次「保護元朗」行動，是「市民再次按耐不住，衝上站台，對示威者一陣圍毆」，有網民稱西鐵不關門「是故意的」，稱看到暴待衝上西鐵列車上打人，「畫面很舒服」，「剛看完直播，很精彩，自由嗨們下周繼續」「我也想去元朗Ｘ死這些港獨狗」​。<br />\n<br />\n中國網民與立法會議員何君堯一樣，將白衣暴徒的惡行英雄化：「元朗昨晚的白衣天使是一群霍元甲呀！」「北有朝陽群眾，南有元朗群眾。元朗加油！」「藤條家法伺候，太剛了！等待大招kill out！」"},{"pid":"281d8c489c3cd75c9e16c7eafe12e5195afdf46e","tid":1346344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190722/59849115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849115&d=kduom0GX2PoGtXVt5SjzIDUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=ace3c9f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190722%2F59849115&h=50be633f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190722/59849115</a>"},{"pid":"29f016453337fdf9e9b87c6951d1c4c8f36fe7fd","tid":1346344,"uid":39205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:52.000Z","msg":"幫手推，宜家係關鍵時期動搖淺藍民意！<br />\n<br />\n【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c7a8366d73948583df9a98f29fa931fd9921279b","tid":1346344,"uid":267969,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"所以香港唔獨立，遲早被支那人虐殺"},{"pid":"4586e3a81864a99ea9ba53e8255b1158e8c0290e","tid":1346344,"uid":24133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c7a8366d73948583df9a98f29fa931fd9921279b","tid":1346344,"uid":267969,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"所以香港唔獨立，遲早被支那人虐殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:05:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060f5f451980d5aae2892921609a2eff665acd8a","tid":1346344,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf092452b1bc3c4ef7dd22c13e4f83e5acc4e1b1","tid":1346344,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:31.000Z","msg":"微博班人弱智架"},{"pid":"4c6c78300694e829f96ec28968c1380858d23b6c","tid":1346344,"uid":37957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c7a8366d73948583df9a98f29fa931fd9921279b","tid":1346344,"uid":267969,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"所以香港唔獨立，遲早被支那人虐殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"民主支那 = 香港最大嘅威脅"},{"pid":"8f57ee6e41bc906991cce80d25d67a948d37b72f","tid":1346344,"uid":68802,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:07:11.000Z","msg":"支那人無一個係無辜"},{"pid":"b9de20d7352ebd8e0904cc351905484cc0d27e07","tid":1346344,"uid":30006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"支那人最想香港死<br />\n佢地明知唔岩都會咁做<br />\n<br />\n因為佢地唔抵得點解同係中國管理<br />\n你地可以有特權<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔爽"},{"pid":"5c69f7e17b23bb1